description: This is a market on whether the price of $TITAN will be above 5 dollars on July 1, 2021, at 12:00 PM ET. The resolution source for this market will be the prices listed on dex.guru (https://dex.guru/token/0xaaa5b9e6c589642f98a1cda99b9d024b8407285a-polygon).  This market will resolve to “Yes” if, according to the resolution source, $TITAN has a candlestick closing price of greater than $5.00 for the date and time of July 1, 2021, 12:00 PM ET. This market will resolve on the “C” (i.e. closing price) listed for the 1 minute candle titled “1 Jul '21 12:00”, with the “1m” tab selected, and the "Candles" display selected, in Eastern (UTC-4) time. To allow for updates, this market will resolve on the number listed for the referenced candle at exactly 12:05:00 PM ET, on July 1, 2021. Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.  If dex.guru is unavailable at the resolution time, another credible source will be chosen in good faith by the MIC to resolve the market. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved in good faith at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
